  "title": "6m Locum Pharmacy Technicians ($20/hr) #HYNT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>• Processes prescriptions and dispenses medications topolyclinic patients in accordance with doctor’s directions as specified in prescriptions</p><p>• Supports Medication Delivery Service (MDS) and PILBOX service for remote collection of medications</p><p>• Provides Tele-dispensing services (where applicable)</p><p>• Assists in video consultation (VC) and medication reconciliation<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>GCE ‘O’ Level with a Certificate in Pharmacy Technician Course (under MOH, PSS or its equivalent) or a Diploma in Pharmaecutical Science </li></ul><p><br /><br />Interested to find out more:</p><p>Please send your resume to: <strong>rehealth@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></p><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Chloe Impens | HR Coordinator| EA License Number: 99C4599<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W</p>",
